  "title": "Warehouse Assistant (Day shift only) - West - WCDT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Manage inbound and outbound logistics processes.</li><li>Prepare and update daily reports.</li><li>Conduct daily inventory cycle counts.</li><li>Coordinate with drivers for urgent deliveries.</li><li>Arrange red rush deliveries when required.</li><li>Handle ad-hoc collections for urgent requests from engineers or call management.</li><li>Process manual releases upon HPE approval.</li><li>Manage EXPO orders during system maintenance periods.</li><li>Verify stock availability through the Easitool website.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc operational tasks as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ol><li>Minimum N-Level qualification.</li><li>Able to read and respond to emails in English.</li><li>Willing to work on weekends and public holidays.</li><li>Responsible, eager to learn, and able to work under pressure.</li><li>Physically fit and capable of handling heavy parts.</li><li>Strong team player with good cooperation and support skills.</li></ol><p><br /></p><p>**Permanent Day Shifts, OT provided!</p><p>**Shift allowance and transport allowance provided!</p><p>**AWS & Bonus is provided!</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd | 20C0270</p><p>Tew Jie Wei | R22106822</p>",
